title: What We Learned at Camp
description: After not receiving participation medals, the Titans must demonstrate what they learned at camp.

title: Hurricane Chata
description: When V & V discover that Chata's emotions control the water in the lake, they use it to their advantage and start their own wave pool business.

title: Fashion Forward
description: When the Fashionistas launch a new line of brainwashing clothing, it's up to the Powerpuff Girls to stop the fashion trend before it's too late.

title: Crazy Mixed Up Puffs/Mizzen in Action
description: Crazy Mixed Up Puffs: The girls must literally work as one to try and stop Mojo from destroying Townsville./Mizzen in Action: Captain Crack McGraigen and his crew are tossed forward in time where discover the chemical X that marks the spot and it is up to the girls and Professor to send the super-charged pirates back to their own time.

title: #LosConejosMágicos
description: Cuando Zee le pide a Kara que cuide a sus dos conejitos mágicos, pronto comienzan a multiplicarse y a desatar el caos por toda Metrópolis.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Summer Wish
description: When Craig decides to keep a lightning bug in a jar, he disrupts the delicate balance of Summer.

title: Time Share
description: Batman and Blue Beetle have to travel back in time to stop Chronos from destroying a young Dark Knight on his very first case.

title: Terminal Velocity Part 1
description: While Windblade is away on a mission, Bee decides to relive a fun memory.

title: Bored to Be Wild
description: Mega Man teams up with his crush, Ashley Adderley, to solve a series of science riddles left by Chemical Man, who's plotting to turn all the city's metal into rubber.

title: Haunted Campfire
description: The campers must battle ghosts of their own creation after their scary stories mysteriously come true.

title: Pizza Hero
description: It's the end of the school year, and as is tradition at Aberdale Elementary, Papa Marianio is slated to dish out his famous pizza along with a spectacle of song and dance. As the kids wait in excitement, they share memories about times with Papa.

title: Zombie King
description: Grundy escapes his Louisiana prison intent on using a magical crystal which will allow him to raise the dead from their graves. Only Batman and Swamp thing stand in the way of his growing zombie army.

title: Memory Part 2
description: Windlbade and Bumblebee are attacked by Decepticons and she regains his trust.

title: O Mother, Where Art Thou?
description: Ma Vreedle threatens to blow up the sun if Ben and the Plumbers don't find her missing son!

title: Infinity Train Trailer
description: What is the train? Where did it come from? And most importantly: What's in the next train car? Join Tulip, One-One, and Atticus in a mind-blowing adventure on the enigmatic Infinity Train.

title: Communicate Openly
description: Bumbleebee becomes the 6th Titan and moves into the Tower but has a hard time adjusting.

title: Suerte
description: When Vic cheats on an enchanted board game, the malevolent characters come to life, and it's up to V & V to figure out how to put them back in the game.

title: Director's Cut
description: Oscar receives a camcorder from his parents and sets out to prove to them the magic on the island is real.

title: Classic Rock
description: Batman thinks he's helping a homeless old man who is being mugged on the street only to discover that the man is a powerful wizard being chased by demons in disguise. It turns out the wizard is on a mission to save Shazam from the clutches of Black Adam.

title: Let's Team Up Because We Aren't Bad Friends
description: The Warriors fear that they've been ignoring their pals, so they team up with Witchy Simone and Noville for a BIG MISSION, only to discover that their friends aren't into it anymore.

title: Block Party
description: Apple and Onion have to outwit a mean duck who's taken over their building's roof.

title: Subterranean Homesick Blues/Honey Struck
description: Subterranean Homesick Blues: The AO return home to learn that no time has passed but they soon discover their knowledge of brawling has gotten years more advanced./Honey Struck: After Strata is sent packing the AO discover that they have picked up a hitchhiker a Panda-like Bakugan who is nothing but sticky trouble.

title: Aspirations
description: The Gangreen Gang is actually committing brilliant crimes. But behind every great gang, there has to be a great woman.

title: Cosmic Bupkiss
description: A storm blocks Oscar and Hedgehog's one chance to see a comet.

title: Big in Japan
description: When Uncle Grandpa and the gang help a kid make a giant monster movie, they cast Mr. Gus as the monster.  But things get tense on the set when Mr. Gus wants to flex his acting muscles while Uncle Grandpa only wants him to flex his monster muscles.

title: Pancake's Bus Tour
description: Apple and Onion go on a guided bus tour as part of their plan to get Apple's shoe back.

title: A Rocky Start
description: The ninja have found their quest! Now they just have to get there, which involves a road trip through the Desert of Doom, a region supposedly inhabited by a giant scarab beetle.

title: Karate Mom
description: After surprising Clarence with Martial Arts classes at the "Aberdojo," Mary gets talked into joining the class herself. She loves the slow-paced lessons in discipline and control, but Clarence just wants to have fun and kick butt! Can Mary convince Clarence to stick with the class, earn his belt and have some fun with her?

title: Lars de las estrellas
description: Lars demuestra estar a la altura.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: La Neblina del Paramo
description: El equipo Tennyson se hace internacional en el Omni-Copter, y la primera parada incluye una caminata por las Tierras Altas de Escocia. Pero el clima no es sólo malo, sino que hay niebla, y eso puede significa solamente una cosa: iel regreso de Niebla!

title: Memory Part 1
description: Windblade tries to help Bumbleebee but he is wary of this "stranger".

title: A Made Up Story
description: Someone is defacing all the posters and statues of Townsville with make-up. Can the girls stop this makeover takeover or will they get the blush off?

title: Tunnels
description: The Bears discover a network of tunnels underneath the cave. Are they prepared to discover where they lead to and who dug them?

title: Now We're Only Falling Apart
description: Pearl tells a story.

title: Lightfall Part 2
description: Lord Obsidian attacks the Lighthouse, but Mega Man overcomes his insecurity and works with his family to repel the big bad, who's rescued at the last second by a mysterious lieutenant, Namagem.

title: Loteria
description: Cuando Vic hace trampa en un juego de mesa encantado, los malvados personajes cobran vida, y V y V son los responsables de averiguar cómo volver a ponerlos en el juego.

title: Hotdog's Movie Premiere
description: Apple and Onion square off against a no-nonsense security guard after they're banned from the premiere of their friend Hot Dog's new movie.

title: #TrianguloDeOdio
description: Cuando la exnovia de Hal aparece en el partido de bienvenida de la preparatoria Metrópolis y se enfurece por amor, convertida en la villana Star Sapphire, Jessica comienza a cuestionar sus propias tácticas no violentas.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Once Upon a Townsville
description: When a dainty princess on a mission comes to Townsville, the girls must learn the superhero way isn't always the right way.

title: World's Best Boss
description: The park guys want to give Benson a World's Best Boss mug.

title: A New Don
description: When Vic & Val discover that Don isn't really himself, it's up to them to use his kooky codex of conspiracies to save him.

title: The Inquisition
description: The students of Elmore Junior High find their world turned upside down when the mysterious school superintendent comes to stamp out their cartoonish ways. But who wants to be normal? Certainly not Gumball and Darwin.

title: Blind Trust
description: Benson has to trust Mordecai and Rigby to get him down a mountain.

title: A Single Pale Rose
description: Steven helps Pearl find her phone.

title: Letters to Lars
description: Steven writes about the latest news of Beach City.

title: Matter of the Mind/Core Cell
description: Matter of Mind: Drago leads the Bakugan against the threat of Tiko to protect a powerful energy source called the Core Cell./Core Cell: The AO defend the Core Cell from an attack by Tiko and in a last ditch effort to save it Dan manages to evolve Drago into his L2 form.

title: Welcome to the Underworld 2
description: After Vic loses a wrestling match, V&V journey to the underworld to seek advice from their uncle, a famous wrestler named El Toro.

title: Moor Fogg
description: Team Tennyson goes international in the Omni-Copter and the first stop is for a hike in the Scottish Highlands, but the weather isn't just bad, it's foggy, and that means one thing and one thing only: the return of The Fogg!

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: A Fistful of Brains
description: Grandpa Max and Rook are looking all over the galaxy for Ben, who is trapped on Khyber's hidden personal hunting preserve.

title: Teletraan X Part 2
description: Investigating a signal in an abandoned missile silo, Bee and Windblade discover their computer back up drone Teletraan X, but it's a trap!

title: Don't Touch
description: Team Tennyson checks out a Samurai Museum in Tokyo, where Ben is too impatient to wait out the Calligraphy experience for the more exciting sounding Samurai one. But when a dangerous Samurai sword is stolen from the exhibit, Ben must take on its thief, the new Big Bad in town, the Forever Knight.

title: Play Date
description: Sick and tired of babysitting Ice King while the Ice Kingdom is being rebuilt, Finn and Jake call up an old friend to hang out with their annoying houseguest: Abracadaniel. But when Ice King and his new BFF accidentally unleash the demon Kee-Oth, Finn and Jake have to clean up their mess.

title: El gran espectaculo
description: Steven filma un documental que sigue los pasos de una banda local mientras consiguen su primer gran oportunidad.

title: The Last Laserdisc Player
description: Mordecai, Rigby, Muscle Man and HFG want to get a laserdisc player so they can watch the director's cut of a cult classic.

title: Dr. Animo and the Mutant Ray
description: Dr. Animo has broken out of jail, and has been tracking down Ben, intent on revenge. At the same time, Ben's broken off a piece of the Omnitrix, and as a result, has turned into weird alien combinations, i.e. StinkArms.

title: Matrix of Leadership Part 1
description: With Windblade captured by the Seekers, Bumblebee is on his own for the first time and is responsible for saving Cybertron.

title: The Hands of Time
description: Master Wu mistakenly tries to single-handedly complete a battle he began decades ago against Acronix, one of the twin Hands of Time. But the arrival of the first Time Blade, a weapon with the power to speed up time, sends the Ninja to the Monastery just in time to rescue their master from certain doom.

title: Back to the Library
description: Uncle Grandpa uses time travel to convince his past self to return a library book on time.

title: Innervasion Part 3: Strange Bedfellows
description: After the Junkbot shoots the Omnitrix and it begins glowing neon-blue, an imprisoned Vilgax explains it is now a gateway through which the Fulmini Empire will invade Earth, but the only way to stop them is from within the Omnitrix, so Ben must team up with the ultimate baddie if he is to save his planet.

title: The Belly of the Beast
description: To repair the Land-Bounty, the ninja must retrieve a critical engine component that has been swallowed by a giant scarab beetle.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Mushroom Menace
description: The Mysterious Hooded Woman wants the Warriors For Hire to defend her giant pumpkin home from the dreaded Smashroom Mushroom, but Vambre and Prohyas can't complete their mission without help from Zombie Pumpkin Magisword!

title: Real Magic
description: Robin dabbles with magic, ignoring Raven's warning that he will anger the magic god.

title: #FightAtTheMuseum
description: Supergirl always relies on her strength, but she'll need more than brawn to stop brainy Catwoman from stealing valuable gems from the local science museum.

title: Whiteout Part 2
description: Windblade flies to the Himalayas to investigate while Bee watches television, acquiring new verbal "samples".

title: 4 on 1
description: Onion's fear of crowds threatens his basketball team's success.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: El club de los solitarios
description: En lugar de celebrar el Día de San Valentín, Vic y Val se atreven a explorar una mansión encantada con sus rivales, Charlene y Piña.

title: Hot Dog estrena su pelicula
description: Cuando unos guardias de seguridad muy serios los echan del estreno de la nueva película de su amigo Hot Dog, Manzana y Cebollín se preparan para pelear.

title: Lightfall Part 1
description: The mysterious Lord Obsidian calls Mega Man a traitor to robots and challenges him to a duel. An overconfident Mega Man is humbled by this mysterious new villain.

title: The Big Sleep
description: When the Professor's latest invention wreaks havoc in the house, it's up to the Powerpuff Girls to stop it before it escapes.

title: Innervasion Part 4: Mind over Alien Matter
description: While inside the Omnitrix, Ben and Vilgax must work together if they are to close the gateway, but once the Fulmini leader, the High Override, appears, even that might not be enough. Luckily, help arrives in the form of a being calling itself Glitch!

title: A Mind Is a Terrible Thing
description: The Warriors easily thwart Phil's latest plan with Legendary Knowledge Magisword so Phil repeatedly tries to steal it from them.

title: The Grid Car
description: Tulip, a headstrong 13-year-old girl, finds a mysterious train where every car contains its own universe.

title: Baby Buktu
description: When attacked in the jungle, Team Tennyson is saved by a toddler who looks eerily similar to Tim Buktu, but when they discover it really is a pint sized version of the nefarious globetrotter, Ben knows there's another threat looming, Nanny Nightmare!

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: KO's Health Week
description: KO spends a week dispensing healthy tips to everyone in the plaza.

title: Sale el Don
description: Cuando Vic y Val descubren que Don Jalapeño no es realmente él mismo, depende de ellos usar el alocado libro de conspiraciones de Don para salvarlo.

title: Una epoca de traidores
description: Lloyd lucha con su papel como maestro en entrenamiento y Nya hace todo lo posible para reiniciar a Zane.

title: Can't Go Back
description: Ronaldo spots something mysterious on the moon, and Steven goes to investigate.

title: Selva lunar
description: Stevonnie se encuentra solo en una aventura.

title: Fractured Part 2
description: Windblade realizes Bumblebee does not remember her and her mission to find the Allspark is critical.

title: Rey del Castillo
description: Ben, Gwen y el Abuelo Max viajan al Castillo Bishopbrook para visitar a un pariente lejano de la realeza. Pero cuando Ben se encuentra con un "fantasma" en la casa embrujada, resulta ser su nuevo rival, Kevin 11, que lanza a alienígenas aún más retorcidos en su camino: iThornblade, Undertow y Materia Oscura!

title: Sabotage Part 2
description: Shockwave creates false memories designed to convince Bee he was always a Decepticon spy.

title: Una linea en la arena
description: Jay lucha por defender la casa de su familia.

title: Huracan Chata
description: Cuando V y V descubren que las emociones de Chata controlan el agua del lago, deciden sacar ventaja y comienzan su propio negocio de piscinas de olas.

title: Teletraan X Part 1
description: The Decepticon Armada is nearing Earth to seek the Allspark and are desperate for clues.

title: Framing Device/Bad Actors
description: Framing Device: When confronted by China Riot Lia learns to evolve Pegatrix after realizing the true meaning behind her filming obsession./Bad Actors: Dan tries to lie about evolving Drago and gets exposed while the team face off against Duran Dane and his unhappy Bakugan Nillious.

title: Los Caza Chicos Malos
description: Izzqy quiere jugar un juego de superhéroes y está dispuesta a hacer lo que sea por ello.

title: Mud Is Thicker Than Water
description: Ben, Gwen and Cousin Lucy try to find out how Psyphon's thugs are getting Plumber technology.

title: Follow that Space Cab!
description: While Superman escorts his prisoner Mr. Mind between planets, he is attacked by Lobo who wants to collect a reward on Mind. Temporarily powered-down, Superman seeks Space Cabbie's help to get away from Lobo.

title: Imaginary Friend
description: The Baby Bears invent an imaginary friend, but the trouble he causes is all too real.

title: Night of the Bat
description: Superman and other Justice League members have to battle Batman when he gets possessed by an evil Djinn, Uthool, who is intent on using the JL power core to blow a crack in Earth.

title: The Kid From 3030
description: The kids meet a mysterious kid from the future and try to help him complete his mission.

title: The Other Side
description: Craig, Kelsey and JP must journey past the Overpass into uncharted territory, the Other Side of the Creek.

title: Cube Part 2
description: Windblade finds it hard to believe that Bee can't remember his favorite sport, Cube!

title: #MeetTheCheetah
description: Barbara Minerva is super-jealous of  "little Miss Perfect" Diana Prince. But when she uses an ancient artifact from her dad's collection to place a curse on Diana, it turns out that Diana's not the one who's cursed. It's Barbara.

title: La Melancolia de Oscar y Erizo
description: Susie organiza el concurso anual de talentos, y todos los campistas compiten para ganar.

title: The Extinction Event Part 2
description: Shockwave orders the Seekers to help him create an extinction event and destroy all organic life on the planet.

title: Lonely Haunts Club
description: Instead of celebrating Valentine's Day, Vic & Val take on a dare to explore a haunted mansion with their rivals, Charlene & Pineapple.

title: Sabotage Part 1
description: From his lab on Cybertron, Shockwave launches an attack on Bee's most vulnerable place...his memories.

title: #AdventuresInBunnysitting
description: Zee asks Kara to look after her two magical bunnies, which quickly start to multiply, wreaking havoc all across Metropolis.

title: The Journey Part 2
description: The Autobots are nearly out of Energon, so they land on a dark planet where they encounter subterranean creatures.

title: Dark Plaza
description: KO and the heroes of the Plaza fight to save Lakewood Plaza Turbo with everything on the line.

title: Siloed Part 1
description: Windblade is playing Cube on Cybertron with Bee when she realizes these are memories and she is still held captive by Slipstream.

title: Cube Part 1
description: Bee discovers a mysterious object in the stolen Decepticon shuttle.

title: Lost in Time
description: Kai and Nya stow away aboard Krux and Acronix's time traveling snake mech in a desperate attempt to save Master Wu. But when they arrive in the past, they must help the Elemental Masters prevent the Hands of Time from literally re-writing NinjaGo history. Meanwhile, the the Ninja remain in the rapidly-shifting present trying to help Kai and Nya's father, who was hit with a Time Punch.

title: I See a Funny Cartoon in Your Future/Octi-Gone
description: I See a Funny Cartoon In Your Future: The girls have the rare task of fighting a medium who is committing petty thefts./Octi-gone: When Bubbles finds a single leg of Octi's, she sets out to find out who took her toy and what they want from her.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: Little Sword of Horrors
description: Prohyas grows a new Magisword from a tiny seed, but doesn't know that his Carnivorous Plant Magisword is a menace to Lyvsherian society until its too late!

title: King of the Dinosaurs Part 1
description: With the help of Teletraan- X, Bee and Windblade excavate an deactivated Autobot that looks like a dinosaur.

title: Bienvenidos al Inframundo Parte 1
description: Después de que Vic pierde una pelea de lucha libre, V&V viajan al inframundo para buscar el consejo de su tío, un famoso luchador llamado El Toro.

title: Delivery Effect
description: Unikitty and gang have ordered some delicious Thai food for dinner.  Unfortunately the wait for the delivery is proving too much, time itself seems to have slowed down. In an effort to get the food their faster the gang utilizes Dr. Fox's time machine, which causes big problems and really hurts Father Time's feelings.

title: I Heart Heartforde
description: Oscar, hedgehog and the other campers are excited to take a trip to the non-magical town of Heartforde.

title: Inglorious Toddlers
description: Owen fears he's about to lose his BFF Noah to a gifted military school.

title: Ramen
description: The Baby Bears help a struggling ramen chef perfect her ramen and save her shop.

title: OK A.U.!
description: An evil warlock takes our heroes to a strange alternate universe.

title: Bananas & Cheese
description: Duncan is determined to stop the musical duo Bananas & Cheese from coming to the daycare.

title: Steven Universe the Movie Trailer
description: Steven thinks his time defending the Earth is over, but when a new threat comes to Beach City, Steven faces his biggest challenge yet.

title: Matrix of Leadership Part 2
description: Bumblebee doubts his abilities as he has to find the Ark to awaken Optimus and the Autobots.

title: Rad's Alien Sickness
description: When our heroes are infected with a virus, Rad stubbornly refuses to back down.

title: Show de momias
description: Duncan sale en una misión para espantar a Courtney durante una excursión al museo.

title: Secrets Discovered
description: Secrets are revealed as Nya confronts the Samurai X imposter, Kai pursues the truth about his parents and the other Ninja desperately seek to locate and rescue Master Wu. But as usual, some answers only lead to more questions.

title: The Mall
description: The Bears go the mall and encounter their human counterparts.

title: Speechless on the Seine
description: While in Paris, France, Ben catches Zombozo robbing the Louvre, but when Zombozo hypnotizes Ben to remain speechless, Ben must navigate a foreign land like a mime in order to stop the criminal clown and his travelling circus.

title: Hic Hic Hooray
description: Bridgette gets the hiccups and becomes desperate to get rid of them.

title: Carroneros
description: Lloyd se da cuenta de que hacerse cargo del debilitado Maestro Wu no es una tarea fácil.

title: Awaken Sleeping Giants Part 1
description: Bee, Windblade and Grimlock finally determine the location of the lost ship, the Ark.

title: Escape from Beyond the Cosmic
description: When Clarence accidentally breaks a local arcade game Jeff has become obsessed with, Clarence puts together his own real-life version of the game at home, encouraging Jeff to act out his fantasy in levels created exclusively by Clarence.

title: The Sidekick
description: During a quest to retrieve a loaned video game, Darwin begins to suspect that he is trapped playing second fiddle to Gumball.

title: The Hatching
description: The Ninja learn more about the Krux and Acronix, the two fallen Elemental Masters known as the Hands of Time, and are sure this threat has finally been eliminated. But with Wu out of action and suffering from the effects of the Time Punch, the Ninja discover a new enemy in their midst, the Vermillion Warriors. And the Ninjas have no idea who controls them.

title: La incubacion
description: Los Ninja descubren un nuevo enemigo en medio de ellos.

title: Maccadam's Part 2
description: Windblade realizes Bee's memory must be coming back - they access the Hivemind and visit three different eras of Maccadam's.

title: Cartas para Lars
description: Steven escribe sobre las últimas novedades de Ciudad Playa.

title: Uncle Grandpa Land
description: Pizza Steve must find a way to sneak onto his own roller coaster at the newly opened Uncle Grandpa Land.

title: Allspark Part 2
description: They search for clues as to the whereabouts of the Allspark and uncover another important memory!

title: The Burden
description: Gumball and Darwin are given the job of looking after the lame school hamster. Principal Brown gives Gumball and Darwin the ancient school hamster, Chris Morris, to look after for the weekend. However they accidentally leave it at school, and take home a clump of Principal Brown's hair instead. Surprisingly they discover it makes an excellent pet!  When they realize they have left the real Chris Morris at school, they have to race to find him before their error is discovered.

title: Tripped Up/Power Tripp
description: Tripped Up: Dan and Wynton stumble on both a possible hidden location of the Mind Core Cell and Colonel Tripp who wants the energy source for himself./Power Tripp: After a falling out with Dan, Wynton is mind-controlled by Tripp who stages an attack to ignite a war between Brawlers and the Military.

title: Scavengers
description: In the midst of an epidemic of mysterious metal thefts by the Vermillion Warriors, Lloyd realizes stepping up and taking over for the ailing Master Wu is not an easy task.

title: Shun Shine/Ronin Son
description: Shun Shine: The AO want to evolve their Bakugan like Dan did with Drago but only Shun finds a way by tapping into the energy of the Mind Core Cell./Ronin Son: When Shun's cousin Masato Kazami claims Hydorous as his intellectual property the AO must battle to keep their friend by their side.

title: Questing For Quests
description: Realizing they have gone soft, the ninja search for a quest to reignite their Spinjitzu training. Unfortunately, NINJAGO City is enjoying a period of rare tranquility.

title: King of the Dinosaurs Part 2
description: Teletraan-X's scans reveal their old friend Grimlock, who is intent on finding the rest of his missing dinosaur friends.

title: Fractured Part 1
description: Windblade discovers Bumblebee in the desert on his own.

title: The Laziest
description: Gumball and Darwin challenge Dad to a "lazy-off."

title: The Climb
description: Craig's phone gets stuck in Mt. Sycamore, the tallest tree in the creek!

title: 4 a 1
description: El temor de Cebollín a las multitudes amenaza el éxito de su equipo de baloncesto.

title: Welcome to the Underworld 1
description: After Vic loses a wrestling match, V&V journey to the underworld to seek advice from their uncle, a famous wrestler named El Toro.

title: Prank War
description: When Master Frown starts a prank war with UniKingdom, the friends are ready to strike back. But Unikitty doesn't really understand pranks, thinking they're too mean. Can the friends help Unikitty comprehend a proper goof and win the prank war with Frown? Or will they be forced to suffer his tricks without retaliation and admit defeat?

title: Saltar del fuego a un mar hirviente
description: Kai y Nya son chantajeados para que usen sus poderes elementales combinados para salvar al Maestro Wu que se desvanece rápidamente.

title: Evil's Encore
description: Dr. Animo reminisces about when he once took control of the Plumber's HQ in Mount Rushmore. (Flashback episode.)

title: Magical Moments: Week 7
description: This week's magical moment is…five new episodes are now unlocked!

title: Atrapa la Botella
description: Manzana y Cebollín inventan un nuevo juego que atrae una atención inesperada.

title: Siloed Part 2
description: Windblade manages to fight her way out when Slipstream is called away and she discovers Bee and Teletraan-X are there to help!

title: Enter the Wood Man
description: Mega Man accidentally awakens Wood Man, who thinks it's still the Hard Age, sets off on a path of destruction toward Silicon City.

title: Fiesta en la Cuadra
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben ser más astutos que un pato malvado que se apoderó del techo de su edificio.

title: #HateTriangle
description: When Hal's ex-girlfriend shows up at the Metropolis High homecoming game and goes love-ballistic as the villain Star Sapphire, Jessica begins to second-guess her own nonviolent tactics.

title: King of the Castle
description: Ben, Gwen, and Grandpa Max next travel to Castle Bishopbrook to visit a distant relative who's royalty, but when Ben encounters a "ghost" at the haunted home, it turns out to actually be his new rival, Kevin 11, throwing even more twisted aliens his way: Thornblade, Undertow, and Dark Matter!

title: Tu mama y la mia
description: Steven lleva a Garnet a conocer a algunos de sus nuevos amigos.

title: Agua de Ensalada Caliente
description: Robin debe salvar a los Estados Unidos de una nueva invasión británica cuando beber té vuelve ingleses a los demás Titanes.

title: Having the Timeout of Our Lives
description: Owen forms a special bond with Duncan after having loads of fun with him during their timeouts.

title: Pausa y efecto
description: Kai se enfrenta a su padre solo para descubrir que sus padres son en realidad cautivos. Mientras tanto, los Ninja trabajan para liberar a Wu, Cyrus Borg y otros cautivos.

title: Ren Faire
description: Clarence and his pals venture to the Aberdale Renaissance Faire. Clarence confuses a medieval play for reality, and vows to stop the evil black knight from getting the princess.

title: The Gym
description: The Bears go to the gym and get quite the work out.

title: Megatron Is My Hero Part 2
description: Bee remembers an early version of Megatron where he was a gladiatorial hero, but realizes how dangerous he became.

title: Megatron Is My Hero Part 1
description: Windblade explains the threat of Megatron and the Decepticons to Bee.

title: Innervasion Part 2: Call the Dream Police
description: After defeating the Warbot and discovering Vilgax inside, Ben's "secret voices" only worsen and begin affecting his sleep, but once Gwen discovers a sleepwalking Ben using missing items from the campsite to create his own massive Junkbot, it is up to Ben to stop his own creation.

title: The Perfect Adventure
description: When Mao Mao gets hungry for the perfect adventure, Adorabat tells a white lie.

title: Eruption Part 1
description: As the Autobots discover the Ark, they have to wake up their friends in this battle for the future.

title: The Attack
description: The Ninja celebrate their escape from the Vermillion Army and their retrieval of the Emerald Time Blade but with Acronix and Krux determined to get their Blade back, the Airjitzu Temple becomes a battleground.

title: Apple Wedding
description: You are cordially invited to the Wedding of the Year! But who will be united in matrimony?

title: Insomnio en el Sena
description: Durante su estadía en París, Francia, Ben descubre a Zombozo en pleno robo en el Louvre. Pero cuando Zombozo hipnotiza a Ben para que se quede sin palabras, Ben debe navegar por una tierra extranjera como un mimo para detener al payaso criminal y su circo ambulante.

title: Beach Episode
description: Surf's up on a wacky beach adventure when our heroes are challenged to the ultimate beach battle.

title: They Lurk Below
description: Max's old friend has built the world's only underwater resort, and Ben, Gwen and Max are invited for a sneak peak. But it turns out in order to power the resort, Max's friend took an energy orb from a race of underwater aliens. Now, the aliens want their energy orb back and destroy the resort in order to get it.

title: Not Without My Fudgy Lumps
description: Noah tries to rescue the chocolates Owen forgot outside.

title: Food Around the Corner
description: Ben as Gravattack attempts to moderate a fragile peace treaty, but must endure the attacks of tiny alien fleas, which have inhabited his body.

title: The Journey Part 1
description: Bee accesses a memory from onboard the Ark on its journey from Cybertron to Earth.

title: Lazer Tag
description: When the Score creeper traps Unikitty and the gang in his laser tag arena the gang must defeat the house team or be imprisoned forever.

title: Bottle Catch
description: Apple and Onion's favorite game attracts some unexpected attention.

title: Shadowstriker Part 1
description: Bee doubts his fighting abilities as he continually loses in practice to Windblade.

title: Operation Tin Man
description: Gizmo convinces the Titans he's kidnapped Cyborg, when in reality Cyborg's just hanging out in the HIVE tower with his girl Jinx. When Gizmo gets annoyed by Cyborg's constant presence, the two start a prank war.

title: Family BBQ
description: Mordecai wants to get a handshake from Margaret's dad.

title: Helado en 60 segundos
description: Después de que a Owen lo engañan en un camión de helados, los niños se unen para solucionarlo.

title: Whiteout Part 1
description: Bee remembers his escape pod from the Ark crashed in the snowy Himalayas.

title: Ultimate Weapon
description: When Max finds out that part of an alien weapon has been unearthed in Texas, he becomes obsessed with finding it. In doing so, he leads Ben and Gwen on a wild adventure.

title: What's Your Problem?
description: Amethyst convinces Steven to take a day off for himself.

title: Pause and Effect
description: Kai confronts his dad for aiding the Hands of Time only to discover his parents are actually Acronix and Krux's captives. Meanwhile, as the Ninja work to free Wu, Cyrus Borg and the rest of the Hands of Time's captives, a third Time Blade arrives, one with the power to temporarily stop time!

title: Allspark Part 1
description: Hiding from the Decepticons, Windblade use her Cityspeaker powers to search Bee's memory files.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Galactic Wonder
description: Wonder Woman has won student of the month at Super Hero High again!  As a special surprise Principal Waller has flown in Wonder Woman's mother, Queen Hippolyta, for a visit. Queen Hippolyta is not happy with what she finds and demands that Wonder Woman return to school at the island paradise of Themyscira. Hoping to take her mind off of her troubles with her mother Wonder Woman, Batgirl and Supergirl decide to investigate a strange electromagnetic anomaly. Their investigation leads them to the hideout of Lena Luthor where they discover a plot between her and Eclipso to transform the planet Earth into a new version of Gemworld!  The girls will have to split up to find the generators scattered around the planet and destroy them. They'll also have to overcome Lena's new breed of mood altering Kryptomites to save the day and convince Queen Hippolyta that Super Hero High is the best school for Wonder Woman!

title: Power Cycle
description: After replicating Elec Man's powers, an underslept/overcharged Mega Man goes on a 24/7 hero spree that ends up turning him into his own worst enemy.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Eruption Part 2
description: Teletraan-X has to reboot the offline computer systems to wake up their Autobot friends and the ship while fighting the Deceptions.

title: A Time of Traitors
description: Kai's investigation of a Vermillion Warrior Helmet leads him to discover Krux is alive and well in NinjaGo, living under an assumed identity. Meanwhile, as the Vermillion Warriors go on a kidnapping spree, Lloyd struggles with his role as master-in-training and Nya does her best to reboot Zane, who was knocked off line in his first battle with the Vermillion.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: Out of the Fire and into the Boiling Sea
description: The Hands of Time blackmail Kai and Nya into using their combined elemental powers to retrieve the fourth and final Time Blade from the Boiling Sea with the promise the siblings can use its reversal power to save the quickly-fading Master Wu. Meanwhile, the Ninja and Cyrus Borg get unexpected help from Samurai X as they attempt to destroy the Hands of Time's time-travelling snake mech before it's operational.

title: Las manecillas del tiempo
description: El maestro Wu intenta completar una batalla que comenzó hace décadas contra Acronix.

title: What's the Big Idea?
description: Pizza Steve and Mr. Gus try to help Uncle Grandpa get an idea.

title: Shadowstriker Part 2
description: Through memory, Bee is shown some of his past triumphs, like rescuing Optimus from Shadowstriker.

title: The Extinction Event Part 1
description: Decepticons Shockwave and Shadowstriker arrive on Earth with a simple plan to find the Allspark.

title: Radio Silence
description: Oscar must get Hedgehog a special sandwich in order to save their friendship.

title: Bienvenidos al Inframundo Parte 2
description: Después de que Vic pierde una pelea de lucha libre, V&V viajan al inframundo para buscar el consejo de su tío, un famoso luchador llamado El Toro.

title: Lost Playground
description: When Aberdale Elementary's beloved playground equipment is replaced with safe, boring alternatives, Clarence and the gang seek out their old playground equipment in the legendary lost playground yard.

title: Uncle Melvins
description: Legendary rock band, the Melvins, team up with Uncle Grandpa to help a young girl who wants to win her school's talent show.

title: Hot Salad Water
description: When drinking tea turns the other Titans English, it's up to Robin to save America from another British invasion.

title: Earth & Water
description: Princess Bubblegum subjects Flame Princess to a series of tests to gauge Flame Princess's fiery tendencies. But when there's an emergency at the treehouse, and Princess Bubblegum leaves Cinnamon Bun to watch Flame Princess, her experiment might literally backfire in her face.

title: Secretos revelados
description: Los secretos se revelan cuando Nya se enfrenta al impostor Samurai X, Kai persigue la verdad sobre sus padres y los otros Ninja buscan desesperadamente localizar y rescatar al Maestro Wu.

title: Big Pinchy
description: JP leads his friends on a voyage to find the biggest crayfish in the creek.

title: Awaken Sleeping Giants Part 2
description: Slipstream and her Seekers engage in battle as our heroes trek towards the Ark.

title: Trapped in Paradise
description: Unikitty and the gang have crashed on a fabulous island. It's really nice and no one wants to leave until Richard convinces them that they need to return to the Kingdom and deal with their responsibilities. Unfortunately every attempt to escape the island is sabotaged. Now they must find the culprit to ensure their return home.

title: Terminal Velocity Part 2
description: Bee finds himself on Velocitron with Hod Rod to have some fun but it turns into a nightmare as the Plague of Rust descends.

title: The BFFS
description: Gumball's old BFF Fuzzy, turns up on his doorstep. Darwin struggles to accept that there was someone before him and fails to contain his jealousy. But is Darwin right to mistrust Fuzzy? Does Fuzzy actually have sinister motives for reconnecting with his old BFF?

title: Blue Ribbon Blues
description: When a famous scientist comes to the school, Blossom will stop at nothing to impress him at the Science Fair even if that means putting Townsville in danger!

title: El Paseo en Autobus de Pancake
description: Manzana y Cebollín suben a un autobús que da un tour guiado como parte de su plan para recuperar el zapato de Manzana.

title: #BurritoBucket
description: Babs loves her job at fast food restaurant Burrito Bucket, but her boss, who's fed up with her chronic lateness and bad case of scatterbrain, would love any excuse to fire her. When a bank robbery breaks out right across the street from work, Babs is torn between her role as a superhero and dutiful Burrito Bucket employee. Will she be able to save the day and keep her job all in the nick of time?

title: Country Club
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to rescue the golf cart from a bunch of rich people at a country club.

title: Dungeon Train
description: All aboard! Finn and Jake discover a train where every car is a dungeon filled with a new foe for Finn to fight. Jake quickly gets bored and wants to leave, but Finn is having the BEST time and doesn't want to leave... ever!

title: Maccadam's Part 1
description: Bee and Windblade avoid an attack by Slipstream and Bee asks to go to Maccadam's!

title: Innervasion Part 1: Message in a Boxcar
description: As Team Tennyson prepares their boxcar for an upcoming race, Ben is hearing voices and is unable to go Upgrade to enhance his car, but once the race is interrupted by a mysterious Warbot, Ben must overcome the voices inside his head if he is to defeat the giant adversary.

title: Wasted True Potential
description: In the wake of the previous season's victory, the ninja have gone soft and Master Wu must remind them of who they truly are.

title: I Love You Mao Mao
description: An explosive loner and his slacker best friend are waylaid from their journey into legend, only to find that their story is just beginning.

title: A Line in the Sand
description: While the Ninja fight to save MegaMonster Amusement Park, Jay struggles to defend his family's home from the Vermillion Warriors. But the arrival of the Emerald Time Blade, with its ability to slow time, leads to a desert chase as the heroes try to reach the Blade before the snakes get it!

title: Jakesuit
description: Jake is sick and tired of Finn using his body as a suit of armor, so he convinces Finn to trade places to show him how much it really stinks.

title: Our Brand is Chaos
description: Bubbles and Buttercup make a deal without realizing the consequences.

title: El ataque
description: Los Ninja celebran su escape.

title: Beep
description: To help combat bummer feelings, Unikitty's installed Bad Vibe detectors throughout the castle. But soon, annoying beeping detectors fill the halls, and they can't find the source of the bad vibes or shut off the sound! It would seem someone's not owning up to being in a bad mood.Will the friends figure out who is secretly a Negative Nancy, or will they lose their mind to beeping madness?

title: Perdidos en el tiempo
description: Kai y Nya se escabullen en un intento desesperado por salvar al Maestro Wu.

title: Sun Scream/City of Frownsville
description: Sun Scream: The girls get the ultimate sunburn and must try to fight crime despite their UV damage./The City of Frownsville: When the tearful Lou Gubrious sets a crying ray on Townsville, the girls must find a way to stop the tears before the town is flooded.
